desktop/src-tauri/target/release/steam_appid.txt
desktop/src-tauri/gen/

# PixelLab per-frame unit exports — packed into sprites.json + packed/ sheets
# by `npm run pack:sprites`. The raw frames and rotation PNGs aren't loaded
# at runtime (the loader reads packed/walking.png, packed/attacking.png,
# packed/rotations.png — sliced into per-direction images on the fly). `**`
# covers both base units (units/<faction>/<unit>/) and promotion variants
# (units/<faction>/<unit>/paths/<path>/), plus any other asset category
# that follows the same pack-from-frames pattern.
client/src/game-portal/src/assets/**/animations/
client/src/game-portal/src/assets/**/rotations/
*.bak